{"tid":1840823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"維園年宵人流較往年少　民間「和你宵」旺丁又旺財","createTime":"2020-01-25T04:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T08:16:15.000Z","uid":236891,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f838fe154e2dbdde4665eef7b5697d45cf3d2b","tid":1840823,"uid":236891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:22:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378041&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378041%26refer%3DShare&d=EXOoM7fQMXhTNR4rfnaZT4lFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=c8b924f4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D378041%26refer%3DShare&h=81098eeb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=378041&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】今年食環署轄下的年宵巿場取消乾貨攤檔，全港最大的年宵巿場維園人流明顯較往年疏落，檔主都提早減價促銷。而民間在多區自發的年宵市場，都出現排隊入場的人龍。<br />\n<br />\n全港最大的年宵巿場維園沒有乾貨攤位，再加上細雨綿綿，往年水洩不通的情景不再。<br />\n<br />\n年宵的花，大家都想帶它們回家。她第一年來維園，就買到心頭好，但仍覺得失望。<br />\n<br />\n人流少了，檔主為求散貨，都提早割價促銷，有攤檔索性提早收爐，她就預了虧本。賣小型盆栽的就吸引到小朋友的目光，生意可能好一點。<br />\n<br />\n來到豬年尾聲，維園年宵的熟食攤位就最多人。有檔主話雖然生意都不及往年，但期望大家新一年豐衣足食。<br />\n<br />\n在荔枝角的一個商場，巿民自發經營年宵巿場，場外有長長人龍排隊等入場，場內人頭湧湧。鼠年主題貨品雖然欠奉，但多了些本土創意，亦毋忘反修例。<br />\n<br />\n有檔主指，在這裏擺檔旺丁又旺財。場內一些遊戲攤檔亦吸引一家大細。<br />\n<br />\n而在大埔「和你宵」，排隊進場的市民排滿這一段大窩西支路，內裏有位置給市民寫上心聲。場內不少貨品與反修例有關，遊戲攤位亦諷刺時弊。<br />\n<br />\n放棄年輕人？睇下你班藍屍幾多消費力先講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095397747a8c3f5e3a68ee4de4dbc9bdb6f63ac9","tid":1840823,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"文匯大公點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac72aca2f1f0888339366e143207566b9ba7f41a","tid":1840823,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"095397747a8c3f5e3a68ee4de4dbc9bdb6f63ac9","tid":1840823,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:26:01.000Z","msg":"文匯大公點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:29:07.000Z","msg":"話黃店呃黃絲水魚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4cfd87d043fea08eae53461858967b0cc3a659e","tid":1840823,"uid":290883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"黃色經濟圈 係站唔住腳的！！"},{"pid":"132b26c46e91dbeaeb601d3f6119c5e601710c0e","tid":1840823,"uid":19437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:30:37.000Z","msg":"銅鑼灣條蛇餅勁過出新iPhone<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269e2ae7131d8d47635c3a9f5dd43f69b9e90929","tid":1840823,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好波！"},{"pid":"c216d7946bee5a4fb8b7d268911d08cde4fda595","tid":1840823,"uid":92002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d1b18009b62a72bbba7ca437565f340da1c4cd1","tid":1840823,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T04:39:45.000Z","msg":"不嬲年青人先係消費力最強。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45dda13d017d79131be1390f775e30e14625fb14","tid":1840823,"uid":38915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T07:21:43.000Z","msg":"今日除左D2仲有無其他地方宵？"},{"pid":"e71708daefb75443b090b5417a2eda7835ff1bd4","tid":1840823,"uid":182519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T08:01:13.000Z","msg":"今日邊度有？"},{"p